'''托马斯·斯科特'''（Thomas Scott，{{bd|1984年||}}）是英国的一名[[YouTuber|YouTuber]]、[[遊戲節目|遊戲節目]]主持人和[[網頁開發者|網頁開發者]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Reddit: Top YouTuber Accuses Brave Browser of Violating His Rights with BAT|url=https://u.today/reddit-top-youtuber-accuses-brave-browser-of-violating-his-rights-with-bat|accessdate=18 May 2020|author=Dovbnya|date=28 December 2018|first=Alex|work=u.today|publisher=U.Today|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126151816/https://u.today/reddit-top-youtuber-accuses-brave-browser-of-violating-his-rights-with-bat|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=YouTuber Tom Scott Pits Creators Against One Another In Game Show Based Around Lateral Thinking|url=https://www.tubefilter.com/2018/05/25/htom-scott-lateral-quiz-show/|accessdate=18 May 2020|author=Gutelle|date=25 May 2020|first=Sam|work=tubefilter.com|publisher=Tube Filter|archive-date=2020-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306225533/https://www.tubefilter.com/2018/05/25/htom-scott-lateral-quiz-show/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。斯科特最著名的成就是他本人YouTube频道上的影片，這些YouTube频道涵蓋历史、科学、技术和语言学等一系列教育視頻。截至2021年3月，斯科特的频道拥有超过8.242亿的浏览量和364万的订阅者<ref name="irish">{{Cite news|title=Here's why you can't see what the world's 'pinkest pink' looks like on-screen|url=https://www.irishnews.com/magazine/science/2017/07/19/news/here-s-why-you-can-t-see-what-the-world-s-pinkest-pink-looks-like-on-screen-1088524/|accessdate=18 May 2020|work=irishnews.com|publisher=The Irish News|date=19 July 2017|archive-date=2017-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213161651/http://www.irishnews.com/magazine/science/2017/07/19/news/here-s-why-you-can-t-see-what-the-world-s-pinkest-pink-looks-like-on-screen-1088524/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

